---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import heroImg from '../../public/images/hero.png';
---

<section class="relative h-[100dvh] w-full overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
  <!-- Background Image with Ken Burns effect -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 scale-110 animate-ken-burns">
    <img 
      src="/images/hero.png" 
      alt="Luxury Custom Furniture" 
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <span class="block font-sans text-bg-cream text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.4em] uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-up opacity-0">
       INICIO
    </span>
    
    <h1 class="font-serif text-bg-cream text-4xl md:text-7xl leading-tight mb-8 animate-fade-up [animation-delay:200ms] opacity-0">
      Muebles a medida con <br class="hidden md:block" />
      <span class="italic">compromiso real y durabilidad extrema.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="font-sans text-bg-cream/90 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 animate-fade-up [animation-delay:400ms] opacity-0">
      Creamos muebles personalizados que se adaptan a tu espacio, estilo y necesidades, trabajando cada detalle con dedicaci贸n, materiales de alta calidad y cumplimiento garantizado.
    </p>

    <!-- Value Props Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12 animate-fade-up [animation-delay:500ms] opacity-0">
      {[
        "Dise帽o personalizado",
        "Fabricaci贸n minuciosa",
        "Instalaci贸n en terreno",
        "Cumplimiento en tiempos acordados"
      ].map((item) => (
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm py-3 px-4 rounded-sm border border-white/10">
          <span class="text-accent-gold"></span>
          <span class="text-bg-cream text-sm font-sans tracking-wide">{item}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-up [animation-delay:600ms] opacity-0">
      <a href="https://wa.me/56945104564" class="inline-block bg-accent-gold text-text-coffee px-10 py-5 font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-luxury">
         Solicita tu cotizaci贸n
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 opacity-50">
    <span class="text-bg-cream text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">Scroll</span>
    <div class="w-[1px] h-12 bg-bg-cream/50 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="w-full h-full bg-accent-gold animate-scroll-line"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .animate-ken-burns {
    animation: ken-burns 20s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
  }

  @keyframes ken-burns {
    from { transform: scale(1.1) translate(0, 0); }
    to { transform: scale(1.2) translate(-2%, -2%); }
  }

  .animate-fade-up {
    animation: fade-up 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1) forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fade-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-scroll-line {
    animation: scroll-line 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scroll-line {
    0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
    100% { transform: translateY(100%); }
  }
</style>
